description:
Parenting Product Reviews is a great way to start thinking about what products you'll need around the house when your baby arrives. Join us as we dive into strollers, travel cribs, high chairs, and even a few books and blogs! 

The ideal student for this course is any new mom or dad, expecting families, or anyone who care for a young baby (or guys gifts for one!). 

One of the biggest benefits of enrollment in this course is that it provides valuable Q&A access to the instructor. You will be able to work through common challenges related to pregnancy and baby products, identifying the best resources, and reducing anxieties during a challenging but important time in everyone's lives. 

This course can be completed in a few days and provides a foundation for further research.
title: Parenting Product Reviews
